A thin stream issues from beneath the root-mass of an ancient tree and trickles eastward through a shallow bed of smooth, dark stones.
The water is cold and perfectly clear, faintly @@rtinged green@@N by the minerals of the deep forest, and the bank on either side is thick with watercress and broad-leafed plants.
